  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947780/extras/92f04d25dfb5871338c1fa51936fb4ea.avif?t=1716387540\" width=616 height=116 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Dashlab!</h2>A time attack game where you dash around rooms and collect buffs and debuffs to complete levels as fast as possible. Dodge the lasers and bullets that try to hurt you and find the fastest route to get the fastest time in each level.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tired of going fast ?</h2>You can also try the <strong>endless mode</strong> that provide <strong>3 difficulties</strong> and the ability to use a <strong>custom song</strong> of your choice! Don't lose the pace as the longer you stay alive the faster the song goes!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947780/extras/92f04d25dfb5871338c1fa51936fb4ea.avif?t=1716387540\" width=616 height=116 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Dashlab!</h2>A time attack game where you dash around rooms and collect buffs and debuffs to complete levels as fast as possible. Dodge the lasers and bullets that try to hurt you and find the fastest route to get the fastest time in each level.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tired of going fast ?</h2>You can also try the <strong>endless mode</strong> that provide <strong>3 difficulties</strong> and the ability to use a <strong>custom song</strong> of your choice! Don't lose the pace as the longer you stay alive the faster the song goes!",
